    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西式建筑林立的小镇——夕渚镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位少年邂逅长有兽耳的女孩们，并与她们一起在同一间咖啡厅打工已有一年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >咖啡店中打工的认真少女──雪村千絵莉</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从兽人之乡远道而来的天真烂漫的巫女──天宫美久栗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >软萌善良的兽人首领──御园莓华</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强硬帅气的游戏家──舞羽娜娜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内向却内心强大的姑娘──百百濑辉夜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年与她们的恋爱故事还在继续。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并且本作增加了全新的篇章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于辉夜的修学旅行，少年与擅长制作团子的姐姐，百百濑美月的关系急剧升温。更有自称神明、且将少年与美久栗召唤至此的此花复活，将要在小镇闹出大新闻！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性十足的同伴们逐渐增加，每天的生活永远不会无聊，今天也要努力工作♪</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>此花</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：北极狼</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >百年前被魔法使封印的兽人。由于无法独自解除封印，故而把男主与美久栗叫来了小镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/8db6e92bcfbe1b2948f90c4917712887.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>百百濑美月</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：荷兰垂耳兔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辉夜的姐姐，小镇甜品店“望月”的店长。作为店长与甜品师的水平无可挑剔，私底下却也有脱线的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/c788d38facc6dbe760e79ead02a9a023.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>雪村千绘莉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：俄罗斯蓝猫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经戒备身为人类却能看见兽人耳朵的主角，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在已经对他信任有加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/2c83af053090bb06908a7a06bc41b65c.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>天宫美久栗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：博美犬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满活力而且黏人，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于不谙世事显得天真无邪、好奇心旺盛的女孩子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/7fc1b45934b35f9b617756cc2f76312d.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>御园莓华</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：贵宾犬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格保守，偶尔却也小闹一通。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时而手持恋爱小说，等待她的“白马王子”，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现憧憬恋爱的少女一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/2350777c408a2af3be28fa668629c58e.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>舞羽娜娜</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：美国短毛猫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精神活泼的女孩子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为人率直，不分对象。因此非常容易相处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夸奖“帅气”比“可爱”更会让她开心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/51452802af442b5c02c65ee6f266aac6.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>百濑辉夜</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物：荷兰垂耳兔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弱气、畏首畏尾的女孩子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偶尔也想要依靠他人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望帮上姐姐的忙，却由于抵触男性，不擅长接客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143300/extras/2e5998df2526911125053c94bff79f39.avif?t=1762809553\" width=510 height=510 /></span></p>",
